## Usage Example

Here's a basic usage example of the `BankAccountCard`:

```tsx
<Canvas>
  <Story name="Default">
    <BankAccountCard
      account={{
        id: "acc-123",
        name: "Business Checking",
        type: "CHECKING",
        subtype: "BUSINESS",
        balance: 12450.75,
        availableBalance: 12200.50,
        currency: "USD",
        accountNumber: "****4567",
        institution: {
          name: "Chase Bank",
          logo: "/logos/chase.png"
        }
      }}
      transactions={[
        {
          id: "tx-1",
          date: "2023-05-15",
          description: "Office Supplies",
          amount: -245.50,
          category: "Office Expenses"
        },
        {
          id: "tx-2",
          date: "2023-05-14",
          description: "Client Payment",
          amount: 1200.00,
          category: "Income"
        },
        {
          id: "tx-3",
          date: "2023-05-13",
          description: "Utility Bill",
          amount: -142.33,
          category: "Utilities"
        }
      ]}
      onViewDetails={() => console.info("View account details")}
      onAddFunds={() => console.info("Add funds")}
      onTransferFunds={() => console.info("Transfer funds")}
      onViewAllTransactions={() => console.info("View all transactions")}
      loading={false}
    />
  </Story>
</Canvas>
``` 